name: BabyEatsFeedingTracker
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby eats
Developer Terms of Use
des: I help you keep track of breastfeeding sessions for your little one by handling the time and durations for each feeding session. All you have to do is tell me to start and stop feedings. To start a new feeding session, you can say 'Alexa, start a left feeding session'. To stop a feeding, say 'Alexa, stop feeding'. This will just pause the timer for the feeding session. Once you have started a feeding session, you can say 'Alexa, start right feeding' to switch to the right side. You can save a feeding session by saying 'Alexa, save feeding session'. The saved feeding session will have the start time, total duration, and end time.
